data.description:
Wow! Hire movers! Indulge in the perfect blend of luxury and coziness at Hollywood's newest gem! Completely remodeled, this residence is a stunning example of contemporary luxury and comfort.This isn't just a remodeled home, it's a carefully crafted masterpiece with an all-new living experience. Updated features, exquisite finishes, and cutting-edge systems throughout. This home sits elevated and equipped with all new impact windows and doors!  That's not all! All new plumbing and electrical, this residence assures the highest quality and components, providing a retreat that exudes both grandeur and coziness.The master suite is a sanctuary of sophistication and style. Offering a spa-like bathroom and custom closets! The backyard is fully fenced and gated, with enough room to put a pool! Making this home a luxurious retreat and private oasis! 

Situated in the heart of Hollywood, this home offers the convenience of being walking distance to the city's finest dining, entertainment and pristine beaches. This address is the perfect balance between an extravagant lifestyle and a cozy retreat.

Don't miss the opportunity to call this move in ready home your own; a place where luxury meets comfort in Hollywood's most sought-after location!
